lead_paragraph: Australia's women, powered by sisters Bronte and Cate Campbell, beat the United States and Canada to win the Olympic 4x100 meters freestyle relay in world record time on Saturday, retaining the title they won in London four years ago.

headline.print_headline: Campbells Power Australia to Record and Relay Gold
